{"title":"Leetcode第35题：搜索插入位置","slug":"2019101701","date":"2019-10-17T14:12:23.000Z","updated":"2020-10-29T05:39:22.235Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019101701.json","excerpt":"题目给定一个排序数组和一个目标值，在数组中找到目标值，并返回其索引。如果目标值不存在于数组中，返回它将会被按顺序插入的位置。","covers":["http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164850.png","http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164835.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>给定一个排序数组和一个目标值，在数组中找到目标值，并返回其索引。如果目标值不存在于数组中，返回它将会被按顺序插入的位置。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>你可以假设数组中无重复元素。<br><strong>示例1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 5<br><strong>输出:</strong> 2</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 2<br><strong>输出:</strong> 1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例3：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 7<br><strong>输出:</strong> 4</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例4：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 0<br><strong>输出:</strong> 0</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">searchInsert</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> target)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> result=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;nums.length;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[i]&gt;=target) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t    \tresult=i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t    \t<span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(result==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\tresult=nums.length;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164850.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题只要做一次遍历，当他大于等于数组某个数的时候跳出循环即可。<br><img src=\"http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164835.png\"></p>\n","more":"<p>你可以假设数组中无重复元素。<br><strong>示例1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 5<br><strong>输出:</strong> 2</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 2<br><strong>输出:</strong> 1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例3：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 7<br><strong>输出:</strong> 4</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例4：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> [1,3,5,6], 0<br><strong>输出:</strong> 0</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">searchInsert</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> target)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> result=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;nums.length;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[i]&gt;=target) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t    \tresult=i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t    \t<span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(result==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\tresult=nums.length;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164850.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题只要做一次遍历，当他大于等于数组某个数的时候跳出循环即可。<br><img src=\"http://image.codertian.cn/image/%E6%89%B9%E6%B3%A8%202019-10-17%20164835.png\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JAVA","path":"api/tags/JAVA.json"},{"name":"算法","path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}